title: Lopez, Larkin Each Score 17 as Nets Beat Pistons 93-83
text:
Published By: NYTimes Pro-Basketball - Today 
Brook Lopez and Shane Larkin each scored 17 points and the Brooklyn Nets beat the Detroit Pistons 93-83 in a preseason game Thursday night....
